The paper proposes a framework for compressing DNNs while meeting a given energy constraint, which is a problem related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed framework involves modeling DNN energy consumption and formulating DNN compression as a constrained optimization problem, which are topics related to neural networks (cs.NE) and control systems (cs.SY).
